Strengthen your male intimate health in a quick & easy way - get a new updated version of Dr. Kegel app!

This major update contains multiple bug fixes, performance improvements & new amazing features that will support you during every moment of your health journey.

Check out new amazing features:
-Make your training process more diverse with a brand new training program & new great exercises;
-Customize the training difficulty to yourself by choosing one of the Difficulty Levels
-Don’t miss your training sessions & make your training process more sustainable by setting Daily Reminders
-Enjoy smoothest user experience with updated design of Dr. Kegel app

As always, if you have any issues or great ideas, please let us know at support@appercut.eu

Yours sincerely,
Dr. Kegel Team
P.S.: If you like our app, please don’t hesitate to rate and review us
